WEBVTT

00:07.257 --> 00:09.717
(Santa Anna): We will divide
the army into multiple divisions

00:09.759 --> 00:13.762
to pursue and destroy what's
left of the rebel army.

00:13.805 --> 00:16.557
I have vital news. Go.

00:16.599 --> 00:18.684
(Whooping)

00:18.727 --> 00:21.228
(Girl screams)

00:21.271 --> 00:22.563
What happened, boy?

00:22.605 --> 00:24.064
Comanche.

00:24.107 --> 00:26.108
Comanches.

00:29.446 --> 00:30.904
(Horses whinnying)

00:30.947 --> 00:32.865
Ahh!

00:32.907 --> 00:35.117
(Santa Anna): This is
not the work of a ghost

00:35.160 --> 00:37.995
This is the work of a man!

00:38.038 --> 00:39.413
Come to relieve me, Tom?

00:39.456 --> 00:42.750
Give me one good reason why I shouldn't.

00:42.792 --> 00:44.251
I can't think of one.

00:47.210 --> 00:48.756
No! (Shrieks)

00:48.798 --> 00:51.006
You want to kill me?

00:52.469 --> 00:54.803
(Houston): Gentlemen, what do you remember?

00:54.846 --> 00:56.805
(All): Remember the Alamo!

01:01.019 --> 01:03.312
I am waiting.

01:03.354 --> 01:04.730
Hyah!

01:04.772 --> 01:07.733
(Dramatic music)

01:10.440 --> 01:14.965
♪ ♪

